actionConfiguration.body:
INSERT INTO customer_contacts (
  customer_contact_name,
  contact_position,
  customer_contact_email,
  customer_id,
  customer_contact_industry,
  customer_contact_website,
  customer_contact_linkedin,
  customer_contact_first_contact,
  customer_contact_last_contact,
  customer_contact_next_contact,
  customer_contact_contact_method,
  customer_contact_test,
  customer_contact_notes,
  contact_is_active
) VALUES (
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_name ?? null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.contact_position ?? j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.Position ?? null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_email ?? null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_id || null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_industry || null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_website || null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_linkedin || null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_first_contact ? moment(j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_first_contact).format('YYYY-MM-DD') : null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_last_contact ? moment(j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_last_contact).format('YYYY-MM-DD') : null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_next_contact ? moment(j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_next_contact).format('YYYY-MM-DD') : null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_contact_method || null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_test || null }},
  {{ j_ccont_ins_jsn.formData.customer_contact_notes || null }},
  1
);
